Galatasaray Agrees to Sell Arda Turan to Atletico Madrid for $18.6 Million

-- B y   A y d a n   E k s i n
-- 
2011-08-10T04:30:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-10/galatasaray-agrees-to-sell-arda-turan-to-atletico-madrid-for-18-6-million.html
Galatasaray Sportif Sinai & Ticari
Yatirimlar AS, the merchandising arm of  Turkey ’s top league
soccer team Galatasaray, reached an agreement to transfer player
Arda Turan to Spain’s Atletico Madrid for 12 million euros and 1
million euros bonus payment.  Galatasaray will also have priority in the possible
transfer of Turan to a Turkish soccer club in the future,
Galatasaray Sportif said in a statement to the Istanbul Stock
Exchange after the market closed yesterday.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Aydan Eksin at 
 aeksin@bloomberg.net  